---
---

<section class="section problems">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="eyebrow">THE PROBLEM //</div>
		<h2 class="section-title">Local AI is powerful. Getting there isn't.</h2>
		<p class="section-lede">
			Running AI locally solves every cloud problem — but building and
			maintaining the stack is a project in itself.
		</p>

		<div class="grid">
			<div class="vignette">
				<div class="icon icon-red">$</div>
				<h3>Cloud costs compound</h3>
				<p>
					GPT-4 runs you $15–60/M tokens. A busy coding agent burns
					through millions a week. The bill grows faster than the value.
					And every token you send is training data you didn't consent to.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="vignette">
				<div class="icon icon-amber">⚠</div>
				<h3>DIY stacks are fragile</h3>
				<p>
					Ollama + Open WebUI + LiteLLM + custom scripts —
					any update can break the chain. You spend more time maintaining
					the plumbing than using the agents.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="vignette">
				<div class="icon icon-red">🔒</div>
				<h3>Privacy is binary</h3>
				<p>
					The moment a request leaves your network, your code, your
					designs, your customer data are someone else's problem.
					Consumer hardware can't change that equation.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="vignette">
				<div class="icon icon-amber">⚡</div>
				<h3>Consumer hardware taps out</h3>
				<p>
					Your laptop's GPU is busy rendering your IDE.
					Phone-class SoCs throttle under sustained inference.
					You need dedicated silicon — not a background process fighting
					for resources.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.problems {
		background: var(--ctx-bg);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
		background: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.08);
		border: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.28);
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--claw-red-text);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.vignette {
		background: var(--ctx-panel);
		border: 1px solid var(--ctx-border);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-lg);
		padding: 1.5rem;
	}

	.icon {
		width: 2.25rem;
		height: 2.25rem;
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-md);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
	}

	.icon-red {
		background: var(--claw-red-dim);
		color: var(--claw-red-text);
		border: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.25);
	}

	.icon-amber {
		background: rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.08);
		color: var(--ctx-warn);
		border: 1px solid rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.2);
	}

	.vignette h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.vignette p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
